I got a pedicure here yesterday and it was perfect. I made an appointment earlier in the day, but they do take walk-ins. The place was clean and the people were very friendly. If you have really callused feet (like me) get the Pamper Me Pedi, you get extra callus treatment and it is totally worth it. My feet are summer-ready now! Top Nails is close to my office, so I'll be coming in regularly from now on.

